  <Fragment slot="what-this-is">
    <p>Bookkeeping is the day-to-day financial recordkeeping that supports everything else in your accounting process. It includes recording transactions, keeping accounts organised, reconciling balances, and making sure your books stay current enough to support reporting, filings, and business decisions.</p>
